<font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">New Server Announced</font><font size="2"> - 02-15-2004 10:16</font><br><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="100%"><font size="2">Due to the increased traffic brought about by the Gates of Discord expansion this week, we’’re pleased to announce the newest EverQuest server, Morden Rasp&#33; This new server is available immediately and is a standard rule set server available for new characters or for character transfer with items (see http://store.station.sony.com/eq_char_item_moves/ ). <br><br>We apologize for the lack of advance notification but it was important for SOE to increase the number of EverQuest servers quickly to insure a great weekend of EQ gaming. To all of our new and returning EverQuest players we would like to extend a warm "Welcome Home". <br><br>Hope to see you online&#33;</font><br><br></td>
</tr>
